alerts.description:
There is a risk of violent storm gusts (Level 3 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 85-105 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 130 km/h

There is a risk of persistent rain (Level 2 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: 45-70 l/m²; in windward areas: < 120 l/m²

There is a risk of heavy persistent rain (Level 3 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: 50-80 l/m²; in windward areas: ~ 100 l/m²

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: 50-60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 70 km/h

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Max. gusts: ~ 65 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 75 km/h
